{"tid":2038324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我撚到個藍屍呆左","createTime":"2020-05-27T13:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T01:55:41.000Z","uid":3204,"like":10,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"42204eb058c46030bfdad86a7dc064a7d399aa4b","tid":2038324,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"話說朝早因為傳聞有大三罷<br />\n咁我就想被罷工 冇出到門口<br />\n知道班黃絲柒左之後 就馬上收到我上司 泰哥既電話問我係邊<br />\n<br />\n我因為驚比上司罵所以即刻趕番去<br />\n去到途中比幾隻藍屍截住我話黑衫死曱甴<br />\n我見佢地咁嬲 我係褲袋拎左支針出黎諗住安撫佢地<br />\n藍屍即刻問我比針佢地做咩 問我係咪n賓<br />\n<br />\n我諗都唔諗就答係<br />\n<br />\n班藍屍全部冇聲出呆撚晒  我就借啲意跑走左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過見到有個工友好似比人拉走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"c1ec5efa46820a999648c045345cae3d52fd9f2e","tid":2038324,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a106fd7199eea45cf963ce7afb06b2dff58cc590","tid":2038324,"uid":8523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"樓豬返開老庇入筷子"},{"pid":"83fc852ab1a9f87ab2fd49d2f0b12024d9ca71da","tid":2038324,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85759ffd8d7ae9815c7fedff3b6c1e4f01e555e","tid":2038324,"uid":17606,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"ching有語言障礙？<br />\n睇晒成篇文都唔明你想表達乜"},{"pid":"193f43a9a5f44b88d97eab21e7300bf623aa27d4","tid":2038324,"uid":204356,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:20:16.000Z","msg":"ching up mud 9"},{"pid":"2e62a1e93242189030ed3539a9efa4c4f3cd0402","tid":2038324,"uid":581,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid"